Zoom Participants Report

Funtions to analyse Zoom participants report file (.csv).

Read & Clean Zoom's Participant File
class_session()
Zoom Class Session Summary
class_students()

class_studentsID()
Zoom Class Students ID Summary
meeting_overview()
Meeting Overview
class_overview()
Class Overview

Zoom Chat

Funtions to parse program Zoom chat file from .txt file to a tibble, and also do some basic analysis.

read_zoom_chat()
Read Zoom Chat File
zoom_chat_extract()
Extract Zoom Chat Elements to Tibble
zoom_chat_count()
Count Zoom Chat Message
